# Examples from GFM

## A

| foo | bar |
| --- | --- |
| baz | bim |

## B

| abc | defghi |
:-: | -----------:
bar | baz

## C

| f\|oo  |
| ------ |
| b `\|` az |
| b **\|** im |

## D

| abc | def |
| --- | --- |
| bar | baz |
> bar

## E

| abc | def |
| --- | --- |
| bar | baz |
bar

bar

## F

| abc | def |
| --- |
| bar |

## G

| abc | def |
| --- | --- |
| bar |
| bar | baz | boo |

## H

| abc | def |
| --- | --- |

